类 Schedule

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aylanetworks.agilelink.framework.Schedule
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class Schedule
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    Class representing a Schedule for a device. This class wraps the AylaSchedule object and provides convenience methods to manipulate, save and fetch schedule information for a device.

    This class supports two schedule "types", a recurring schedule and a timer. The recurring schedule does not expire, and
